imdb.plot outline: From students to superstars, RANETKI follows a group of high school girls who struggle to balance the demands of homework, friendship, and...oh yeah, becoming a world-famous pop rock band! Join them on their journey which starts as a dream, before becoming reality after signing a major record deal.
